{"tid":779861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己有躁狂症","createTime":"2018-08-14T16:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T08:31:16.000Z","uid":2021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef98d0005194d776a2a5cfe124803524ccff354","tid":779861,"uid":2021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mindpro.hk/%E8%BA%81%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmindpro.hk%2F%25E8%25BA%2581%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E7%2597%2587%2F&d=ypmzyxijdUPvV7XhVUVVfL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=73da04cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mindpro.hk/%E8%BA%81%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前俾屋企人屌話我買好多野 用左好多錢 我發覺自己控制唔到自己去買野 返工又要做雙面人 只有買野個時先覺得係開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上面條link 所有symptoms 都中哂 但又唔想去睇精神科醫生 唔想去接受自己真係有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇巴絲可以俾少少意見我 我真係唔知點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dcbb73ba1b48bb0cf4b7ab70df547d9a0ee3e8","tid":779861,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"減肥先"},{"pid":"016cb64836f9142315004220907d04f7c63adcca","tid":779861,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"唔好殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd53d6785c8e4ccd9da086756d7265e9993d9bf","tid":779861,"uid":2021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016cb64836f9142315004220907d04f7c63adcca","tid":779861,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"唔好殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"咁我又唔會 只係有時會諗不如自己死左去算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"